---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Insights" description="Research and perspective from the front lines of agentic AI. Whitepapers, case studies, and analysis from the world's first AI-native consulting firm.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-pure-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-teal text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Thought Leadership</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight max-w-3xl">
        Research and perspective from the front lines of agentic AI.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-silver max-w-2xl">
        We publish what we learn — from running our own AI-native firm and from advising the enterprises that are building theirs. No recycled analyst reports. No safe takes. Positions backed by evidence and operational experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Content -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-pure-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">Featured</p>
      <div class="bg-navy rounded-2xl overflow-hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-0">
        <div class="p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-teal/15 text-teal rounded-full w-fit mb-6">Whitepaper</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pure-white tracking-tight mb-4">
            The Agentic Enterprise: A C-Suite Guide
          </h2>
          <p class="text-silver text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            The next wave of AI value will not come from copilots. It will come from autonomous agents that execute complex business processes end-to-end. This whitepaper provides the framework for enterprise leaders ready to act.
          </p>
          <a href="/insights/agentic-enterprise-whitepaper" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-teal text-pure-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors w-fit text-lg">
            Download Free Guide
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center bg-navy-light p-14">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-48 h-64 bg-navy rounded-lg border border-silver/20 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-2xl">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-teal mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
              <p class="text-pure-white text-sm font-semibold px-4">The Agentic Enterprise</p>
              <p class="text-silver text-xs mt-1">C-Suite Guide</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">All Content</h2>
      <p class="text-slate text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">Whitepapers, case studies, and articles on agentic AI strategy, architecture, and deployment.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Card: Whitepaper 1 -->
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light p-8 flex flex-col hover:shadow-lg hover:border-silver transition-all duration-200">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal rounded-full w-fit mb-5">Whitepaper</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">The Agentic Enterprise: A C-Suite Guide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">The framework for enterprise leaders ready to move beyond copilots to autonomous agents that execute complex business processes end-to-end.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-silver-light">
            <a href="/insights/agentic-enterprise-whitepaper" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Download
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3" /></svg>
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs text-silver font-medium">Gated</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Whitepaper 2 -->
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light p-8 flex flex-col hover:shadow-lg hover:border-silver transition-all duration-200">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal rounded-full w-fit mb-5">Whitepaper</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Why Our AI-Native Firm Is the Best Proof of Agentic ROI</h3>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">The strongest evidence that agentic AI works is not a vendor demo — it is a functioning organization. We open the books on how Nexus operates.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-silver-light">
            <a href="/insights/ai-native-firm-proof-of-roi" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Download
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3" /></svg>
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs text-silver font-medium">Gated</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Case Study -->
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light p-8 flex flex-col hover:shadow-lg hover:border-silver transition-all duration-200">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-navy/10 text-navy rounded-full w-fit mb-5">Case Study</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">How an AI-Native Firm Built Itself from Scratch</h3>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">From concept to operational firm in under one week. Nine AI agents, five service lines, enterprise-grade deliverables. The full story.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-silver-light">
            <a href="/insights/how-ai-native-firm-built-itself" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Read Now
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs text-teal font-medium">Free</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Article 1 -->
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light p-8 flex flex-col hover:shadow-lg hover:border-silver transition-all duration-200">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-navy/10 text-navy rounded-full w-fit mb-5">Article</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Why Your AI Pilots Are Not Scaling</h3>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">Enterprise AI is stuck in pilot purgatory. The problem is not the technology — it is the gap between proof of concept and organizational reality.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-silver-light">
            <a href="/insights/why-ai-pilots-not-scaling" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Read Now
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs text-teal font-medium">Free</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: Article 2 -->
        <div class="bg-pure-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light p-8 flex flex-col hover:shadow-lg hover:border-silver transition-all duration-200">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-navy/10 text-navy rounded-full w-fit mb-5">Article</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Designing an AI Workforce: What We Learned</h3>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">What happens when you build an entire organization around AI agents — and what those lessons mean for enterprises designing human-AI teams.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4 border-t border-silver-light">
            <a href="/insights/designing-ai-workforce" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Read Now
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs text-teal font-medium">Free</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
